item.title: CVE-2024-29121|2024-03-19T14:48:08.978Z -- Firassaidi -- WooCommerce License Manager
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in Firassaidi WooCommerce License Manager allows Reflected XSS.This issue affects WooCommerce License Manager: from n/a through 5.3.1.
